# 案例1

原sql：

~~~sql
SELECT
	count(
	DISTINCT ( dbr.external_user_id )) 
FROM
	tb_department_bind_relation dbr
	RIGHT JOIN (
	SELECT DISTINCT
		( cst.external_user_id ) 
	FROM
		tb_customer cst 
	WHERE
		customer_status = '0' 
		AND add_time BETWEEN '2020-01-01 00:00:00' 
		AND '2021-11-20 00:00:00' 
		AND user_id IN ( SELECT DISTINCT ( user_id ) FROM tb_user_department WHERE main_department IN ( 4, 5, 7, 9, 14 ) ) 
	) vt ON dbr.external_user_id = vt.external_user_id 
WHERE
	dbr.create_time BETWEEN '2020-01-01 00:00:00' 
	AND '2021-11-20 00:00:00' 
	AND dbr.deleted = '0'
~~~

	count(

	JOIN tb_department_bind_relation dbr ON cst.external_user_id = dbr.external_user_id

	AND '2021-11-20 00:00:00'
